EXECUTIVE SUMMARY 
Session held to define the technical scope for a Debt Collection and Negotiation project. The goal is to implement a hybrid conversational journey using generative AI and human support to recover payments.

PROJECT CLASSIFICATION 
Vertical: Financial Services and Fintech. 
Use Case: Debt Collection and Negotiation. 

TECHNICAL SCOPE

Hybrid Journey: Automated flows using Bot Studio combined with Generative AI (LLM) for flexible negotiation.
Campaign Management: High-scale active messaging via Campaign Manager for collection notifications.
API Integrations: Bot will be integrated with client APIs for debt lookup, agreement terms, and payment generation such as Pix.
Human Support: Multi-channel handoff via Agent Assist for up to 20 agents on WhatsApp and Instagram.
Analytics: Daily (D-1) report exports via FTP for integration with the client's internal BI.

COMMERCIAL AND OPERATIONAL TERMS

Monthly Platform Fee: R$ 22,800.
Professional Services: 50 hours of support and implementation included per month.
Human Agents: 20 seats included in the base platform fee.
Number Management: No additional cost for adding new numbers under the same corporate ID (CNPJ).
Data History: Standard retention of 2 years for conversations and reports.

EXECUTIVE SUMMARY 
Session held to define the technical scope for a Debt Collection and Negotiation project. The goal is to implement a hybrid conversational journey using generative AI and human support to recover payments.

PROJECT CLASSIFICATION 
Vertical: Financial Services and Fintech. 
Use Case: Debt Collection and Negotiation. 

TECHNICAL SCOPE

Hybrid Journey: Automated flows using Bot Studio combined with Generative AI (LLM) for flexible negotiation.
Campaign Management: High-scale active messaging via Campaign Manager for collection notifications.
API Integrations: Bot will be integrated with client APIs for debt lookup, agreement terms, and payment generation such as Pix.
Human Support: Multi-channel handoff via Agent Assist for up to 20 agents on WhatsApp and Instagram.
Analytics: Daily (D-1) report exports via FTP for integration with the client's internal BI.

COMMERCIAL AND OPERATIONAL TERMS

Monthly Platform Fee: R$ 22,800.
Professional Services: 50 hours of support and implementation included per month.
Human Agents: 20 seats included in the base platform fee.
Number Management: No additional cost for adding new numbers under the same corporate ID (CNPJ).

internalActivities.description:
Babyshop UAE, part of the flagship Landmark Group and an existing customer, has requested a feature feasibility assessment for an upcoming project.

·       The requirement is for our Agent Assist to support real-time interaction between customers and in-store Personal Shopping Experts (PSEs) via a AA app.

·       They want to launch this in two markets to start with which is UAE and KSA.

This requirement is primarily for KSA PSE who will be using our AA app -

·       Since a large portion of customers primarily speak Arabic in KSA, while not all PSEs are fluent in Arabic, the client requires an AI-powered translation mechanism. This will automatically translate customer messages from Arabic to English for the assigned PSE, and translate the PSE’s English responses back to Arabic for the customer, ensuring seamless communication without language barriers.
